review_data: Reviewed in the United States on March 29, 2020
name: Kate Miller
title: Lovely yogurt!
review: This is, hands down, the best greek yogurt on the market. Fage, 0% Greek Yogurt is the BOMB.First off, it travels well. There is no clotting of the yogurt or breakage of the packaging. The yogurt stays cold thanks to Amazon Fresh methods and comes just like a grocery store would have it.Next, the taste and texture are divine. It is so thick and creamy, and just perfectly tart. It goes perfectly on any savory dish as a sour cream replacement, or on a sweet dish like a thick whipped cream. I love adding frozen berries, vanilla extract, and cocoa powder or stevia to truly make a fabulous yet healthy dessert.No other greek yogurt is as protein-packed, nonfat, and low carb at this one. I have changed thanks to this wonderful FAGE product! YAY FOR FAGE!

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on April 21, 2018
name: Trancelucence
title: My FAVORITE Greek Yoghurt
review: I've been using this for years- my favorite Greek non-fat yoghurt, and I've tried many brands.The thickest, firmest, the most like thick sour cream, spoonable and luscious tasting.And it STAYS that way, lasts a long time and I notice much less accumulation of liquid than other brands (virtually none).I use this to make stroganoff, noodles romanoff, on rice, in and on Mexican and Indian foods, as a dip and dip base, on microwave quesadillas, I'd be lost without it.A bargain, and Fresh carries it, yay!
